Output scale_generator.gif

Require echo

Set PlaybackSpeed .8
Set Height 400

Type "./scale_generator"
Enter 1
Sleep 4

Type "Y"
Enter 1
Sleep 4

Type "N"
Enter 1
Sleep 2

Type "./scale_generator -b"
Enter 1
Sleep 4

Type "Y"
Enter 1
Sleep 4

Type "N"
Enter 1
Sleep 2

Type "./scale_generator --bpm"
Enter 1
Sleep 4

Type "N"
Enter 1
Sleep 3